membership:
We are a member of COBCOE, an independent non-profit organisation representing 35 British chambers of commerce across Europe. Acting as an umbrella organisation, COBCOE works with member chambers to advance international trade and business with the United Kingdom. As such, it gives a voice to about 6,000 businesses, mainly located outside of the UK, from all sectors of trade and industry involved in business with the UK.&#xd;
&#xd;
Its aim is to protect and promote international trade. To do this, COBCOE liaises closely with the UK government and other organisations.
